$PROBLEM translated from babelmixr2 ; comments show mu referenced model in ui$getSplitMuModel
$DATA pk.turnover.emax4.csv IGNORE=@
$INPUT ID TIME EVID AMT DV CMT DVID RXROW
$SUBROUTINES ADVAN13 TOL=6
$MODEL NCOMPARTMENTS=4 COMP(DEPOT, DEFDOSE) ; depot COMP(GUT) ; gut COMP(CENTER) ; center COMP(EFFECT) ; effect
$PK MU_1=THETA(3) MU_2=THETA(4) MU_3=THETA(8) MU_4=THETA(9) MU_5=THETA(10) KTR=DEXP(THETA(1)) ; ktr <- exp(tktr) KA=DEXP(THETA(2)) ; ka <- exp(tka) CL=DEXP(MU_1+ETA(1)) ; cl <- exp(tcl) V=DEXP(MU_2+ETA(2)) ; v <- exp(tv) EMAX=1/(1+DEXP(-(THETA(7)))) ; emax <- expit(temax) EC50=DEXP(MU_3+ETA(3)) ; ec50 <- exp(tec50) KOUT=DEXP(MU_4+ETA(4)) ; kout <- exp(tkout) E0=DEXP(MU_5+ETA(5)) ; e0 <- exp(te0) A_0(4)=E0 ; effect(0) = e0
$DES DCP=A(3)/V ; DCP = center/v RXDZ001=(EC50+DCP) IF (RXDZ001 .GE. 0.0 .AND. RXDZ001 .LE. 0.000001) THEN RXDZ001=0.000001 END IF IF (RXDZ001 .GE. -0.000001 .AND. RXDZ001 .LT. 0.) THEN RXDZ001= -0.000001 END IF PD=1-EMAX*DCP/RXDZ001 ; PD = 1 - emax * DCP/(ec50 + DCP) ;effect(0) defined in $PK block KIN=E0*KOUT ; kin = e0 * kout DADT(1) = - KTR*A(1) ; d/dt(depot) = -ktr * depot DADT(2) = KTR*A(1)-KA*A(2) ; d/dt(gut) = ktr * depot - ka * gut DADT(3) = KA*A(2)-CL/V*A(3) ; d/dt(center) = ka * gut - cl/v * center DADT(4) = KIN*PD-KOUT*A(4) ; d/dt(effect) = kin * PD - kout * effect CP=A(3)/V ; cp = center/v
$ERROR ;Redefine LHS in $DES by prefixing with on RXE_ for $ERROR RXE_DCP=A(3)/V ; DCP = center/v RXDZE001=(EC50+RXE_DCP) IF (RXDZE001 .GE. 0.0 .AND. RXDZE001 .LE. 0.000001) THEN RXDZE001=0.000001 END IF IF (RXDZE001 .GE. -0.000001 .AND. RXDZE001 .LT. 0.) THEN RXDZE001= -0.000001 END IF RXE_PD=1-EMAX*RXE_DCP/RXDZE001 ; PD = 1 - emax * DCP/(ec50 + DCP) RXE_KIN=E0*KOUT ; kin = e0 * kout RXE_CP=A(3)/V ; cp = center/v RX_PF1=RXE_CP ; rx_pf1 ~ cp RX_PF2=A(4) ; rx_pf2 ~ effect ; Write out expressions for ipred and w RX_IP1 = RX_PF1 RX_P1 = RX_IP1 W1=DSQRT((THETA(6))**2+(RX_PF1)**2*(THETA(5))**2) ; W1 ~ sqrt((pkadd.err)^2 + (rx_pred_f_)^2 * (prop.err)^2) IF (W1 .EQ. 0.0) W1 = 1 RX_IP2 = RX_PF2 RX_P2 = RX_IP2 W2=DSQRT((THETA(11))**2) ; W2 ~ sqrt((pdadd.err)^2) IF (W2 .EQ. 0.0) W2 = 1 IPRED = RX_IP1 W = W1 IF (DVID .EQ. 2) THEN IPRED = RX_IP2 W = W2 END IF Y = IPRED + W*EPS(1)
$THETA (6.2405e-07 ) ; 1 - tktr (-3.0064e-06 ) ; 2 - tka (-2.004 ) ; 3 - tcl (2.0519 ) ; 4 - tv (0, 0.09858) ; 5 - prop.err (0, 0.51162) ; 6 - pkadd.err (6.4185 ) ; 7 - temax (0.14076 ) ; 8 - tec50 (-2.9535 ) ; 9 - tkout (4.5704 ) ; 10 - te0 (0, 3.7171 ) ; 11 - pdadd.err
$OMEGA 0.078585 ; eta.cl $OMEGA 0.050823 ; eta.v $OMEGA 0.18427 ; eta.ec50 $OMEGA 0.0083632 ; eta.kout $OMEGA 0.0027456 ; eta.e0
$SIGMA 1 FIX
$ESTIMATION METHOD=1 INTER MAXEVALS=100000 SIGDIG=3 SIGL=12 PRINT=1 NOABORT
$COVARIANCE
$TABLE ID ETAS(1:LAST) OBJI FIRSTONLY ONEHEADER NOPRINT NOAPPEND FILE=pk.turnover.emax4.eta
$TABLE ID TIME IPRED PRED RXROW ONEHEADER NOPRINT NOAPPEND FILE=pk.turnover.emax4.pred
